❯ fix C-1

  Read 1 file

The fix is to replace the hard-coded string with String.fromEnvironment, which reads from --dart-define=API_BASE_URL=… at build/run time. I'll keep a local-dev fallback (10.0.2.2 — the Android emulator loopback to the host machine) so the app still builds without the flag on a development machine.

